news.news: Robinson-Earl (ankle) is available for Friday's game versus the Wizards.
news.analysis: Robinson-Earl has been upgraded from questionable to available Friday after missing New Orleans' previous two contests due to a left ankle sprain. Robinson-Earl has averaged 4.4 points, 3.6 rebounds and 1.1 assists in 15.5 minutes across his last 10 appearances.
